And so they banged each other forever after. Well, seems after one hell of a long wait, it is done. I’m personally happy it’s completed, ending was relatively satisfactory. Had some interesting plot devices and was indeed enjoyable. Rather interesting Sakuraya couldn’t fight herself forever and just gave into it despite knowing the truth, oh well. Most of you wouldn’t care, but I still wonder what would’ve happened to Akane (Teppei’s sister), past her chapter. Would’ve been curious how that played out once everyone was banging Kotetsu. A bit interesting to tie this world to the first Older Sister Experience Doujin, though it really wasn’t focused on much. Whatever be, this doujin was a good read 224 pages and all

I don't even remember last time i saw this(incomplete),maybe 9 months/1 year ago,while the story is catching as in the past,the final made me nervous for various reasons. At the end no one ever see 'adult' Teppei,no one looks for him,neither the sis...since she said too that 'loves him',after a whole week..why she didn't try find him? Moreover,Fujino is still around,things may still happen in another doujin (the possible "2" of this). I think this one deserve it,there are some holes in the story that can be filled with some bonus pages. Still...can't blame Teppei at all,while i was in a mixed school,actually 6/7 of students were girls in my class,i admit i am kinda dense,but sometimes i regret saying "no" or "sorry" to some of them due feeling "out of place" like Teppei itself in the start of the doujin. I can say i was truly stupid,to not at least try open myself to them beside friendship,and i still regret. Still 10/10 for this book,deserves it. Everyone here...have a good day.
